title: Frederick Forsyth - The Cobra Disc 03
description:
Somehow disc 3 was corrupt and anyone who downloaded the Cobra audiobook will be greeted by clicking noise when the file for disc 03 is played.
This is a good copy of that disc with same naming convention. Just delete the old disc 03 mp3 and insert this one. With apologies. 

For some reason my first attempt at this repair did not work. This one should be fine. Double apologies.
